    <Descriptive_Notes>
      <Descriptive_Note>
        <Note_Text>The act, process, or policy of prohibition of the production, distribution, circulation, or access to a work, or the suppression or deletion of parts of a work, on the grounds that the work contains material or is of an appearance considered politically or morally offensive by some.</Note_Text>
